<a href="https://www.youracclaim.com/org/ibm/badge/node-js-community-member-level-ii">
<img src="https://acclaim-production-app.s3.amazonaws.com/images/6bebc2d3-8ad5-4592-bbeb-f1a87af54b1f/Node-js%2BMember%2B-%2BLevel%2BII.png"
