	<td style="width:60%;vertical-align:middle;text-align:left;font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;helvetica neue&#39; , &#39;helvetica&#39; , &#39;arial&#39; , sans-serif;>
		<p><font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
		<p><font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif"><strong>How do I earn an IBM Cloud badge?</strong></font></p>
		<p dir="ltr">In most cases, you will be required to complete a learning activity along with an end-of-course assessment. In some cases, you may be required to complete multiple learning activities and assessments, or submit evidence of your qualification depending upon the badged activity.</p>
	</td>
